ng I was living with family nearby and could walk or get a cheap London Tube journey to most venues.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999996521183, \"rank\": 3.474846655413369e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Underground\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"London Tube\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Underground\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Underground\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the expense\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"most venues\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After 2016 games were held far away in Rio and the 2020 Tokyo games were hit by the pandemic,Paris 2024, just a jump across theChannel, seemed attractive.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.8310084636998969, \"rank\": 0.20335717827432787, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999995224576427, \"rank\": 4.775426544102785e-07, \"text\": \"2020 Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1153, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.054308702652814e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2016 games\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"just a jump\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"theChannel\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking into purchasing tickets, I had been bamboozled by the bizarre ticketing system the French authorities have set up.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1307, \"end\": 1313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5570386820498133, \"rank\": 0.7951271876556718, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"purchasing tickets\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"the bizarre ticketing system\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to purchase tickets for a minimum of three separate events.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"a minimum\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"three separate events\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although annoying, this in itself would not have deterred my sporting stubbornness, but the prospective costs of hotels and travel have given me the financial hump.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my sporting stubbornness\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"the prospective costs\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"hotels\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"the financial hump\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eurostar single journeys from St Pancras are up to \\u00a3300 and decent hotels have exploited demand economics to be priced at around \\u00a3500 per night.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.306550863110265e-13, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"St Pancras\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"decent hotels\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"demand economics\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic motto is \\\"Citius, Altius, Fortius\\\" which is Latin for \\\"Faster, Higher, Stronger\\\".\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1743, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Citius, Altius, Fortius\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\"}, {\"begin\": 1743, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Citius, Altius, Fortius\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\"}, {\"begin\": 1743, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Citius, Altius, Fortius\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_symbols\"}, {\"begin\": 1777, \"end\": 1782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin\", \"score\": 0.999999571069203, \"rank\": 4.2892129582385e-07, \"text\": \"Latin\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic motto\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know the Latin for \\\"pricier\\\", but the Olympic movement could consider adding \\\"Expensivus\\\" to reflect the cost of spectators getting to events.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1833, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin\", \"score\": 0.999999571069203, \"rank\": 4.2892129582385e-07, \"text\": \"Latin\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"pricier\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic movement\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Expensivus\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"the cost\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, does attending live sport require you to always remortgage your home?\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"live sport\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2002}, {\"ngram\": \"your home\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, there are ways of being relatively frugal.\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every other year, I have friends Whatsapping me saying that they caught my face on the BBC attending Centre Court at Wimbledon.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2182, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.7110340139209003, \"rank\": 0.4064024789460986, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 2196, \"end\": 2208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Centre Court\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"my face\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, there are pricey ballot tickets, debenture holders and even press passes, but my method involves something more traditional than Friday fish and chips: the Wimbledon queue.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pricey ballot tickets\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"debenture holders\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"even press passes\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"my method\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday fish\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2368}, {\"ngram\": \"chips\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"the Wimbledon queue\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Me and whichever family member I can drag along, leave at the crack of dawn to join the queue for a \\u00a330 Wimbledon ground pass (think Henman Hill).\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2535, \"end\": 2546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henman_Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Henman Hill\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henman_Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henman_Hill\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whichever family member\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"the crack\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"dawn\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"the queue\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\u00a330 Wimbledon ground pass\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eventually we join another queue for resale tickets for Centre Court.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2605, \"end\": 2617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Centre Court\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another queue\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"resale tickets\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Usually around 6pm, I get to stroll into Centre Court for an additional \\u00a315.\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2660, \"end\": 2672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Centre Court\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Compared to my Olympics experience, football in London is somehow a relatively more affordable proposition.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2745, \"end\": 2751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999996521183, \"rank\": 3.474846655413369e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my Olympics experience\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2741}, {\"ngram\": \"a relatively more affordable proposition\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As an east Londoner, I was only ever going to bleed the claret and blue of football club West Ham.\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an east Londoner\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"the claret\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"blue\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"football club\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My family have shared a pair of club season tickets for over two decades.\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My family\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2933}, {\"ngram\": \"club season tickets\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2956}, {\"ngram\": \"over two decades\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It works out historically at about \\u00a3500 for me, given the amount of games I attend.\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 3062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since I have become an education ambassador for West Ham's charitable foundation, I was fortunate enough to celebrate with the club's first team players on the balcony of Old Stratford Town Hall as we lifted our first major silverware since 1980 in 2023 with the Europa Conference League.\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3117, \"end\": 3120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4996300789062984e-17, \"text\": \"Ham\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ham\"}, {\"begin\": 3334, \"end\": 3351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2959362244398072e-32, \"text\": \"Conference League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an education ambassador\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"the club's first team players\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"the balcony\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"Old Stratford Town Hall\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3258}, {\"ngram\": \"our first major silverware\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was most certainly a money can not buy experience.\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a money\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3384}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the women's football game, I have managed to snag tickets for as low as \\u00a320 for the FA Cup final at Wembley.\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3515, \"end\": 3522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wembley_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9999999903347998, \"rank\": 9.325219688322595e-09, \"text\": \"Wembley\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wembley_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wembley_Stadium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's football game\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3440}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though I paid substantially more to cry into my overpriced Wembley Stadium beer as our men's team lost on penalties to Italy in Euro 2020.\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3643, \"end\": 3648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9023689422340496, \"rank\": 0.10819406891487415, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\"