ates\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has reminded me of the 1890 novelThe Picture of Dorian Gray.\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 1890 novelThe Picture\", \"from\": 4509, \"to\": 4534}, {\"ngram\": \"Dorian Gray\", \"from\": 4538, \"to\": 4549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Author Oscar Wilde famously wrote, \\\"Nowadays people know the price of everything and the value of nothing.\\\"\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4564, \"end\": 4569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1380021432037355e-16, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"the price\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4617}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4621, \"to\": 4631}, {\"ngram\": \"the value\", \"from\": 4636, \"to\": 4645}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, I am sometimes prepared to pay beyond the odds for attending live sport like at London 2012.\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4745, \"end\": 4756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999997476152, \"rank\": 2.5237924124273556e-10, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the odds\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4711}, {\"ngram\": \"live sport\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The memories (and the photos to show off) last a lifetime.\", \"from\": 4759, \"to\": 4817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The memories\", \"from\": 4759,